    public class BinaryLogisticRegressionTrainingSummary
extends BinaryLogisticRegressionSummary
implements LogisticRegressionTrainingSummary
    :: Experimental :: Logistic regression training results.

    param: predictions dataframe output by the model's transform method. param: probabilityCol field in "predictions" which gives the probability of each class as a vector. param: labelCol field in "predictions" which gives the true label of each instance. param: featuresCol field in "predictions" which gives the features of each instance as a vector. param: objectiveHistory objective function (scaled loss + regularization) at each iteration.
